# Mysterious Facts App

A web application that displays random mysterious and interesting facts from around the world. The app features a clean, modern interface with smooth animations and a glass-morphism design.

## Features

- Random fact generation with titles and descriptions
- Smooth transition animations
- Responsive design for all devices
- Glass-morphism UI elements
- Gradient background

## Project Structure


## Setup Instructions

1. Clone or download this repository
2. Open `index.html` in a web browser
3. Click the "Generate Fact" button to display random mysterious facts

## Customization

You can customize the app by:

1. Adding new facts in the `facts` array in `script.js`
2. Modifying the color scheme in `style.css`
3. Adjusting the layout and sizing in `style.css`

## Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6+)

## Browser Support

- Chrome (latest)
- Firefox (latest)
- Safari (latest)
- Edge (latest)

